<div class="container explore-container">
    <div class="text-center explore-text">
        <p>
            Greenery is for those who love planning just as much as they love gardening. Leveraging Trefle, a global plants API, you’ll have the chance to learn more about plants, especially plants native to your current garden’s location. 
            <br/>
            <br/>
            Like a plant? Save it to your garden and utilize our tracker to keep notes on your plants progress! 
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="text-center explore-form">
        <form action="/explore/plants" method="GET">
            <strong>
                <label for="plantName">Search a plant:</label>
            </strong>
            <input class="explore-input" type="text" name="q" id="plantName">
            <input class="btn landing-btn" type="submit" value="Search">
        </form>
    </div>
</div>